00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:13.600
Tapi kamu...

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:15.560
Saya tidak tahu

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:19.800
bahwa Anda menipu saya.

00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:23.240
